00:07:06.480 --> 00:07:12.880
underlying water table, you take samples of the water, send them to the lab for analysis,

00:07:12.880 --> 00:07:18.799
and they come back with the concentrations of the various different solutes, so xylene,

00:07:18.799 --> 00:07:26.480
